<h2 class="bold font-l">Indy Drags On</h2>
<p class="_pmvv-vidbox-descTxt">
During the truck chase, Indy gets thrown out of the windshield of his truck. He manages to grab onto the grille, but the driver attempts to crush him using the car ahead. To avoid this, Indy hangs on to the bottom of the truck, lets himself down to the back, and climbs back on. </p>
</div>
<div class="video-examples-thumbs">
<a href="#video-link" data-video-id="llctkq" data-video-descrip="Sideshow Bob parodies the classic scene in Cape Fear, in order to follow the Simpsons to their next destination. Which does work, though he has to suffer through many speed bumps, hot coffee and a drive through a cactus patch." data-video-title="Sideshow Bob does Cape Fear" data-video-url="https://d1w6li7s85ibls.cloudfront.net/qvbr/llctkq_640x360p_qvbr.mp4" data-video-thumbnail="https://static.tvtropes.org/trope_videos_transcoded/images/sd/llctkq.jpg" data-video-trope="Main/UndersideRide" data-video-tropename="Underside Ride" data-video-approval="APPROVED" data-video-troper-rating="" data-video-average-rating="" data-video-rating-count="" data-video-media-sources="WesternAnimation/TheSimpsons,Recap/TheSimpsonsS5E2CapeFeare" class="video-launch-link video-overlay-link video-background-image lazy-image" data-src="https://static.tvtropes.org/trope_videos_transcoded/images/sd/llctkq.jpg">
<p><span class="bold">Sideshow Bob do...</span></p>
